        {
            "title": "美國消費者信心跌至接近紀錄低點 個人財務看法惡化",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 由於美國人對個人財務狀況的看法惡化，美國消費者信心在11月跌至接近歷史最低水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據密西根大學公佈的數據，11月消費者信心指數降至51，10月為53.6。最新數字僅略高於初值。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當前狀況指標下滑7.5點至51.1的紀錄低點。對個人財務狀況的看法為2009年以來最為暗淡。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/oMC7rlQLKgGTIsIAH2Hasg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/5d32665f6e05e9cf13290e3282fafa7a\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「消費者對物價居高不下和收入走弱仍然感到沮喪，」調查負責人Joanne Hsu在聲明中表示</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周五公佈的數據顯示，消費者預計未來一年通膨率為4.5%，連續第三個月放緩。預計未來五到十年通膨率每年將達到3.4%，低於10月預估的3.9%。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3c9e6b89-4a38-31bb-8d4a-2e6af1afc013-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管美國人對通膨的擔憂有所緩解，但他們仍然對高昂的生活成本和就業保障感到焦慮。報告顯示，對自己失業可能性的預期升至2020年7月以來的最高水平。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本次調查於11月3日至11月17日之間進行。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Consumer Sentiment Falls to Near Lowest on Record (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%B6%88%E8%B2%BB%E8%80%85%E4%BF%A1%E5%BF%83%E8%B7%8C%E8%87%B3%E6%8E%A5%E8%BF%91%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E4%BD%8E%E9%BB%9E-%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA%E8%B2%A1%E5%8B%99%E7%9C%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%83%A1%E5%8C%96-154632392.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-22 12:05:47",
